-- San Diego Padres Give Manager Bud Black a Three-Year Contract Extension
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-19T17:27:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/san-diego-padres-give-manager-bud-black-a-three-year-contract-extension.html

          
          
             The San Diego Padres have given
manager Bud Black a three-year contract extension through 2013,
the team said.  
 The Padres are 54-37, and lead the National League
Western Division by four games over the Colorado Rockies.  
          
          


  


        